name: Cello Technologies Seattle
tag_list: home-theater, media-rooms, home-automation, home-network-integration, distributed-audio--video, acoustic-design, lighting-control, integrated-security
overview:
Cello specializes in designing, installing and supporting home theater,audio/video, light management, home automation, communications and network systems for high end residential projects, large yachts and specialized commercial applications (presentation spaces, board rooms and houses of worship). We work both in new structures as well as remodel/retrofit situations. Cello’s projects are concentrated in the Northwest US, but span the US and world.

For our yachting customers we are supported by a worldwide network of preferred service providers.
